title: Draft Room Traps; Go Get My Lunch Draft Edition
itunes:title: Draft Room Traps; Go Get My Lunch Draft Edition
description:
A room filled with heroes- Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Gregg Rosenthal and Marc Sessler return in one piece from the ATN bachelor party in southern California and give a full recap of what went down this weekend. The Raiders sent scouts home before the draft (8:40) and the Cardinals screen their final "feeler calls" leading up to the big weekend. (14:45). The heroes break down all the rest of the news in the NFL including the Bills backfield looking crowded with the recent signing of TJ Yeldon. (20:03) Go get my lunch draft edition brings up some spicy takes including the Browns trading back up into the first round. (29:50)
